title: Afterburn 3.2 for 3ds Max 2008 (32-bit version)
description:
This is Afterburn 3.2 for 3ds Max 2008.  There is a keygen included, along with a readme file.  Some people may not even need the keygen (for some reason, at least on my computer, it just worked.)

This also may work with 3ds Max 9, but I&#039;m not sure.  You can try it and see if it does.
